title: MMA fighter calls out porn star, she fires right back at him (5 Photos)
text:
View as Slideshow 1 
Chael Sonnen is known to be one of the biggest trash talkers in sports, with his creative and witty one-liners and comebacks. During a press conference for Bellator 170, an event he is fighting Tito Ortiz in, he was not afraid to call out Ortiz’s ex-girlfriend Jenna Jameson. 
App users click HERE to watch video below. 2 A video posted by MMAFighting.com (@mmafightingdotcom) on Jan 19, 2017 at 2:19pm PST 3 
Jameson, the former porn star who’s earned millions of dollars in her career, is well known for her talents and is not ashamed of it either. 
She fired back at Sonnen. 4 5 
Swing and a miss for Sonnen. He’s going to have to get more creative than that according to Jenna. Advertisement
